## Execute Swap via CLI

```bash
initiad tx move execute 0x1 dex swap_script \
    --args '["object:0x...", "object:0x...", "u64:100", "option<u64>:100"]' \
    --from [key-name] \
    --gas auto --gas-adjustment 1.5 --gas-prices 0.015uinit \
    --node [rpc-url]:[rpc-port] --chain-id [chain-id]
```

